IntelliJ IDEA

Ctrl + Alt + L :    Reformat code
Alt + Enter :       show fix suggestions
F2 :                jump to next failure in code
Alt + 1 :           show project window
Ctrl + E :          show recent opened Files
Ctrl + B :          go to declaration
Ctrl (twice) :      Run Anything window
Ctrl + / :          Add/Remove Line Comment
Ctrl + Shift + / :  Add/Remove Block Comment
Shift (twice) :     Find Action / Functions / Classes / Files / shortcuts / ...